Allen Payne ( born July 7 , 1968 in Harlem , New York City , New York ) is an American film and television actor . Allen 's first exposure on television was in 1990 on the sitcom The Cosby Show , and on its spin - off A Different World in 1992 . During two seasons , he made several appearances portraying the character Lance Rodman . He also appeared as Marcus Stokes in an episode during season two of The Fresh Prince Of Bel - Air . Allen has appeared in many films , including New Jack City and Jason 's Lyric . He has also studied dance . He currently stars in Tyler Perry 's House of Payne . 